  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>
    We do not collect, store, or share any personal data from users of the NM26 mobile application.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Collection</h2>
  <p>
    This app does not use analytics, advertising, or tracking SDKs. No personal information is collected or transmitted to third parties.
  </p>

  <h2>Camera Access</h2>
  <p>
    The camera is used solely for:
    <ul>
      <li>Avatar photo uploads (user-initiated)</li>
      <li>QR code scanning (system-level or browser-based)</li>
    </ul>
    Camera data is never stored or transmitted by the app.
  </p>

  <h2>Firebase Usage</h2>
  <p>
    NM26 uses Firebase for app functionality (e.g. saving avatars or settings), but no personal data is collected without your knowledge.
  </p>

